text: The Senior women's race at the 2017 IAAF World Cross Country Championships was held at the Kampala in Uganda, on March 26, 2017. The exact length of the course was 9,858 m (33m start, 4 full laps of 2,000 m and a final lap of 1,825m). Complete results for individuals.
